                                "markdown": "Mako templates do not provide a global HTML escaping mechanism. This means you must escape all sensitive data in your templates using '| u' for URL escaping or '| h' for HTML escaping. If you are using Mako to serve web content, consider using a system such as Jinja2 which enables global escaping.\n\n<b>References:</b>\n - [Semgrep Rule](https://github.com/PyCQA/bandit/blob/b1411bfb43795d3ffd268bef17a839dee954c2b1/bandit/plugins/mako_templates.py)\n - [https://docs.makotemplates.org/en/latest/syntax.html#expression-escaping](https://docs.makotemplates.org/en/latest/syntax.html#expression-escaping)\n - [https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/en/2.11.x/intro/#](https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/en/2.11.x/intro/#)\n",
                                "text": "Mako templates do not provide a global HTML escaping mechanism. This means you must escape all sensitive data in your templates using '| u' for URL escaping or '| h' for HTML escaping. If you are using Mako to serve web content, consider using a system such as Jinja2 which enables global escaping."
